text: Ottman Azaitar (born February 20, 1990) is a Moroccan-German-French mixed martial artist. He competes in the Lightweight division of the Ultimate Fighting Championship. He has won the BRAVE Combat Federation Lightweight championship one time. == References == == Other websites == * Ottman Azaitar Profile at UFC.com * * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Mixed martial artists Category:Sportspeople from Cologne Category:French mixed martial artists
